basisset.dc:title: SARC-DKH
basisset.dc:description:
All-electron scalar relativistic basis sets for third row transition metal atoms
Dimitrios. A. Pantazis,(a) Xian-Yang Chen,(b) Clark R. Landis,(b) and Frank Neese(a)
(a) Lehrstuhl fur Theoretische Chemie, Institut für Physikalische und Theoretische Chemie,Universit?t Bonn, Wegelerstr. 12, D-53115 Bonn, Germany, (b) Department of Chemistry, University of Wisconsin—Madison, 1101 University Avenue, Madison, Wisconsin 53706, USA. The SARC-DKH basis sets are segmented all-electron scalar relativistic basis sets in which the coefficients of contracted GTOs have been optimized for use with the DKH2 scalar relativistic Hamiltonian.
